    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 11th level, when you have both your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.fAibWIlBW7I5kFuf]{Astral Arms} and @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.TO5fasMvBTJ1uYJv]{Visage} summoned, you can cause the body of your astral self to appear (no action required). This spectral body covers your physical form like a suit of armor, connecting with the arms and visage. You determine its appearance.</p>\n<p>While the spectral body is present, you gain the following benefits.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.4b2tR7EGkZbci5N4]{Deflect Energy}. You can reduce certain damage taken.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.QrALT7RZAiNNZJXp]{Empowered Arms}. Once per turn you can deal additional damage with your astral arms.</p>",
